OL,6,GThe BBC wants #22.3 million back from
OL,7,GArqiva following the transmitter mast
OL,8,Gfire that knocked out TV and radio
OL,9,Gsignals across North Yorkshire,
OL,10,GTeesside and Durham Coast.
OL,12,FThe fire at Bilsdale transmitting
OL,13,Fstation in August 2021 resulted in
OL,14,Fhouseholds losing access to services.
OL,15,FSome locations were without a signal
OL,16,Ffor months. The BBC was forced to
OL,17,Foffer licence fee refunds for
OL,18,Faffected users.
OL,3,CBBC demand #22.3m in damages in
OL,4,CArqiva lawsuit
