OL,6,FDetails of the lawsuit first emerged
OL,7,Fin The Telegraph earlier this month,
OL,8,Fbut didn't provide details of the
OL,9,Fmonetary extent of the claim against
OL,10,FArqiva. The claim is for loss of
OL,11,Fservice and other credits the BBC
OL,12,Fsays is due under the terms of its
OL,13,Fexisting contracts with Arqiva.
OL,15,FArqiva says it has taken legal advice
OL,16,Fand is defending the claim. The
OL,17,Fcompany in turn has raised an
OL,18,Finsurance claim and expects to be
OL,19,Fable to recover some, but not all of
OL,20,Fthe liabilities and costs incurred by
OL,21,Fthe fire and the subsequent rebuild
OL,22,Fof Bilsdale transmitting station.
OL,3,CBBC demand #22.3m in damages in
OL,4,CArqiva lawsuit
