OL,6,FOn 22nd May, the first TV signals
OL,7,Fwere switched on at the new Bilsdale
OL,8,Fmast. In the coming weeks the full
OL,9,Fset of TV, radio and mobile services
OL,10,Fwill migrate to the mast, finally
OL,11,Frestoring reception levels to those
OL,12,Fexperienced before the fire.
OL,14,FArqiva was blamed for poor
OL,15,Fcommunication in the aftermath of the
OL,16,Ffire.  As anger over the prolonged
OL,17,Foutage grew, Arqiva's PR stepped into
OL,18,Faction, with The Guardian's Jim
OL,19,FWaterson interviewing Arqiva's boss
OL,20,FPaul Donovan, blaming the local
OL,21,Fterrain and roads for the delays with
OL,22,Frestoration work.
OL,3,CBBC demand #22.3m in damages in
OL,4,CArqiva lawsuit
