OL,6,FOfcom's incident review, published in
OL,7,FJune 2022, took a dim view of the
OL,8,Fmatter, saying Arqiva should have had
OL,9,Fa site-specific deployment plan
OL,10,Fready.
OL,12,FThe Bilsdale site is understood to be
OL,13,Fcosting more than #50,000 a month to
OL,14,Frun.
OL,3,CBBC demand #22.3m in damages in
OL,4,CArqiva lawsuit
